instructions: Welcome to Magic Forest!
Your first task is to collect all the
crystals and find the exit to the next level.
Tip: To zoom-in, use key 'A', to zoom-out use key 'Z'.
Good Luck!
Great job! But now things become more difficult.
Be careful and don't let yourself fall down into the abyss!
Tip: Use keys 'X' and 'C' to change your camera view
Now, things become more interesting. Take a look up!
See that fellow?  He is not so harmless as he looks.
You better watch out for him!
Good job. Be careful of the floor!
Some parts of it might stay for awhile,
but then it'll collapse beneath your feet!
These elevators go a long way up, but don't be scared
of heights! Your hard work will reward you.
You did awesome on the last level!
Tip: Use the ice crystals to help freeze
the green reptile.
Tip: The teleporters will help you move fast.
Use bombs to destroy your enemies.
Tip: Just press the 'B' key to throw the bomb.
You are deep in the forest!
Tip: Use your teleports carefully!
Some floors here will fall, so watch your way.
Are you ready for a run? Let's get to it!
You made it! You are one step closer.
Good Luck!
